label: Homicides + Socio-Economics (1960-90)
detail: Homicides and selected socio-economic characteristics for continental U.S. counties. Data for four decennial census years: 1960, 1970, 1980 and 1990.

label: San Francisco Crime Incidents (2012)
detail: Incidents of robberies, drugs/narcotics possession or sale, vehicle theft, and vandalism for July 1 to December 31, 2012

label: Moral statistics” in 1830s France
detail: Classic social science foundational study by Andre-Michel Guerry on crime, suicide, literacy and other “moral statistics” in 1830s France

label: 2017 Unemployment Rates for U.S. Counties
description: 2017 Labor force information for U.S. Counties
detail: This dataset contains 2017 labor force information from the [Bureau of Labor Statistics](https://www.bls.gov/lau/#tables) joined with county shapefiles from the [Census Bureau](https://www.census.gov/geo/maps-data/data/cbf/cbf_counties.html).
